Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，妳還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個下雪的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一邊等爸爸回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊一起做雪人，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍晚歸的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且摸我的頭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要爸爸愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼事情都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊，深優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說無可取代的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是靠"重視"這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法完全徹底說明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的半身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠讓大家都幸福的黃金時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經融化消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不覺得寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為再找一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起重做一個就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊等爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪白閃耀的世界…


